    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1936-09-26T05:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1936-09-26T05:00:00-05:00" n="458"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d458">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">851.5151/999: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in France</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Wilson</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Extract]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1936-09-26T11:00:00+01:00"
                            >September 26, 1936—11 a.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received September 26—9:51 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>926. From Cochran. At about 1 o’clock this morning the Minister of Finance of
                    France gave to the press the French text of the declaration on monetary policy
                    which was being made simultaneously with the American and British corresponding
                    declarations.…</p>
                <p rend="center">. . . . . . . . . . . . . .</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <list>
                            <item>[Cochran]</item>
                            <item>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Wilson</hi>
                            </item>
                        </list>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
